i         ---------- Efficacy of Magick ---------- 		gopher.black	70
i		gopher.black	70
0[7] Efficacy of Prayer	/Efficacy of prayer	gopherpedia.com	70
i		gopher.black	70
iUsing the framework we've established, we can use the more		gopher.black	70
imainstream magickal practices to explore the scientific		gopher.black	70
iinvestigations of occult phenomena. In the link above, there is		gopher.black	70
ia wealth of information about the difficulties in statistical		gopher.black	70
iinference and falsifiablity, measurability in general, and		gopher.black	70
ia survey of the types of studies that have been done. I'd strongly		gopher.black	70
irecommend reading that page cover-to-cover with an open mind.		gopher.black	70
i		gopher.black	70
iThe most striking thing to me about the challenges of study and		gopher.black	70
ithe measurability of outcomes is that we must take a sacred		gopher.black	70
iactivity and measure it by elements that are profane (to use the		gopher.black	70
iterms of Mircea Elliade). Ultimately the change that should occur		gopher.black	70
iis a profane one, though. It must be concerned with the material		gopher.black	70
iworld or else we're using our mind to change our mind, which		gopher.black	70
idoesn't seem to fit our narrow definition of magick. Perhaps using		gopher.black	70
iyour mind to change the mind of another could fit, but the method		gopher.black	70
iwould be the key deliniation (batting your eyes and winking can		gopher.black	70
icertainly create new thoughts in someone else but is that		gopher.black	70
imagick?).		gopher.black	70
i		gopher.black	70
iIf our outcomes are limited to the physical then they are		gopher.black	70
imeasurable. What comes next is to determine what action of will		gopher.black	70
ican create these effects at a significant rate above a control.		gopher.black	70
iThis is a very rigorous way to avoid issues of the Baader-Meinhof		gopher.black	70
iphenomenon or other cognative biases.		gopher.black	70
i		gopher.black	70
iSo what do studies of that have to say? From the article above,		gopher.black	70
ia "systemic review of intercessory prayer reported inconclusive		gopher.black	70
iresults, noting that 7 of 17 studies had 'small, but significant,		gopher.black	70
ieffect sizes' but the review noted that the three most		gopher.black	70
imethodologically rigorous studies failed to produce significant		gopher.black	70
ifindings". Overall, there's just not a lot of rigorous research		gopher.black	70
ibeing done. Even if we did have reliable results, prayer		gopher.black	70
irepresents only a small fraction of the occult magickal practices		gopher.black	70
iin the world, and prayer itself has thousands of forms and formats		gopher.black	70
ito consider.		gopher.black	70
i		gopher.black	70
iSo where do we go from there? Let me start by pointing out that		gopher.black	70
iafter thousands of years of advancement and the advent of western		gopher.black	70
imedicine, the Chinese still widely practice their traditional		gopher.black	70
imedicine. That alone speaks to its efficacy. The west is bringing		gopher.black	70
iover learnings from China every day.		gopher.black	70
i		gopher.black	70
iAnd that brings me to my next point: occult practices are occult		gopher.black	70
ibecause they are unknown. The paranormal describes things outside		gopher.black	70
iof normal experience. Occult practices once included metalurgy.		gopher.black	70
iWhat we don't fully understand is often ignored and denegrated		gopher.black	70
irather than explored and investigated. There is a staggering		gopher.black	70
iamount of knowledge we have confirmed through science only		gopher.black	70
ihundreds of years of casual practice. As an example, the entire		gopher.black	70
ifield of optics existed and flourished for centuries before we		gopher.black	70
iunderstood the science of shaping glass.		gopher.black	70
i		gopher.black	70
iOur understanding of the effects may be limited, but out		gopher.black	70
iunderstanding of the method is almost completely absent. In one of		gopher.black	70
ithe prayer studies there was no significance in those prayed for		gopher.black	70
ivs those not, but there was a lift in those that knew they were		gopher.black	70
ibeing prayed for. Perhaps when it comes to immune responses we		gopher.black	70
ihave a greater power to manipulate the physical in ourselves than		gopher.black	70
iin others through will alone. Perhaps this one of the infinite		gopher.black	70
ivarieties of action wasn't the specific one needed.		gopher.black	70
i		gopher.black	70
